Question: Each image contains one tablet-type device, and one image shows the device with the screen inverted.

Reference Answer: False

Right image URL: https://www.gizbot.com/img/2016/08/17-1471439717-gelfrog.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many tablet-type devices are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many tablet-type devices are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the screen inverted?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the screen inverted?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER1} == 1 and ({ANSWER2} xor {ANSWER3})')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER4)
```
